Package: smscollectr
Title: Collect and Process Rain Gauge SMS Data
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: person("Ousmane", "Ouedraogo", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "ouedraogo.ousmane@meteoburkina.bf")
Description: Reads structured SMS messages forwarded to a Google Sheet by
    field observers, detects and fixes malformed entries, and parses valid
    messages into tidy rainfall and agrometeorological observations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    googledrive,
    googlesheets4,
    tibble,
    tidyselect,
    dplyr, 
    keyring,
    purrr,
    rlang
URL: https://github.com/oousmane/smscollectr, https://oousmane.github.io/smscollectr/
BugReports: https://github.com/oousmane/smscollectr/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
